<hr data-start="6390" data-end="6393">
<h2 data-start="6395" data-end="6435">4. Static Structure / Typing (Sketch)</h2>
<p data-start="6437" data-end="6500">We sketch a simple typing discipline. You can reuse it in Lean.</p>
