<h3 data-start="6733" data-end="6760">4.2 Typing Environments</h3>
<ul data-start="6762" data-end="6884">
<li data-start="6762" data-end="6792">
<p data-start="6764" data-end="6792"><code data-start="6764" data-end="6767">Γ</code> maps variables to types.</p>
</li>
<li data-start="6793" data-end="6829">
<p data-start="6795" data-end="6829"><code data-start="6795" data-end="6798">Σ</code> maps sphere ids to interfaces.</p>
</li>
<li data-start="6830" data-end="6884">
<p data-start="6832" data-end="6884"><code data-start="6832" data-end="6835">Δ</code> maps ports to types (local to a scope / region).</p>
</li>
</ul>
