<p data-start="5036" data-end="5049">with actions:</p>
<ul data-start="5051" data-end="5099">
<li data-start="5051" data-end="5099">
<p data-start="5053" data-end="5099"><code data-start="5053" data-end="5072">α ::= τ | emit(p)</code> (internal or pop emission)</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="5101" data-end="5170">Time evolution and field propagation are handled separately (see §6).</p>
<h3 data-start="5172" data-end="5192">5.1 Pop Emission</h3>
<p data-start="5194" data-end="5274">First, we need a big-step evaluation for pop expressions to concrete parameters.</p>
<p data-start="5276" data-end="5489">Let <code data-start="5280" data-end="5287">⟦E⟧_σ</code> be the value of expression <code data-start="5315" data-end="5318">E</code> under environment <code data-start="5337" data-end="5340">σ</code> (mapping term variables to semantic values). Similarly, <code data-start="5397" data-end="5418">⟦RFunExpr⟧_σ ∈ RFun</code>, <code data-start="5420" data-end="5439">⟦AmpExpr⟧_σ ∈ Amp</code>, <code data-start="5441" data-end="5462">⟦ModeExpr⟧_σ ∈ Mode</code>, and <code data-start="5468" data-end="5488">⟦PopExpr⟧_σ ∈ Pops</code>.</p>
<p data-start="5491" data-end="5553">We will write simply <code data-start="5512" data-end="5523">⟦PopExpr⟧</code> assuming a fixed environment.</p>
<p data-start="5555" data-end="5575"><strong data-start="5555" data-end="5575">Rule (POP-EMIT):</strong></p>
<p data-start="5577" data-end="5601">If <code data-start="5580" data-end="5595">⟦PopExpr⟧ = p</code>, then</p>
<span class="katex-display"><span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" display="block"><semantics><mrow><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mtext>pop(PopExpr)</mtext><mo separator="true">,</mo><mi mathvariant="normal">Π</mi><mo stretchy="false">)</mo><mover><mo stretchy="true" minsize="3.0em">→</mo><mpadded width="+0.6em" lspace="0.3em"><mrow><mtext>emit</mtext><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mi>p</mi><mo stretchy="false">)</mo></mrow></mpadded></mover><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mn>0</mn><mo separator="true">,</mo><mi mathvariant="normal">Π</mi><mo>⊎</mo><mo stretchy="false">{</mo><mi>p</mi><mo stretchy="false">}</mo><mo stretchy="false">)</mo></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">(\text{pop(PopExpr)}, \Pi) \xrightarrow{\text{emit}(p)} (0, \Pi ⊎ \{p\})</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height: 1.397em; vertical-align: -0.25em;"></span><span class="mopen">(</span><span class="mord text"><span class="mord">pop(PopExpr)</span></span><span class="mpunct">,</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right: 0.1667em;"></span><span class="mord">Π</span><span class="mclose">)</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right: 0.2778em;"></span><span class="mrel x-arrow"><span class="vlist-t vlist-t2"><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height: 1.147em;"><span style="top: -3.322em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height: 2.7em;"></span><span class="sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight x-arrow-pad"><span class="mord mtight"><span class="mord text mtight"><span class="mord mtight">emit</span></span><span class="mopen mtight">(</span><span class="mord mathnormal mtight">p</span><span class="mclose mtight">)</span></span></span></span><span class="svg-align" style="top: -2.689em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height: 2.7em;"></span><span class="hide-tail" style="height: 0.522em; min-width: 1.469em;"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="400em" height="0.522em" viewBox="0 0 400000 522" preserveAspectRatio="xMaxYMin slice"><path d="M0 241v40h399891c-47.3 35.3-84 78-110 128
