<p data-start="9449" data-end="9469">via the rules of §5.</p>
</li>
<li data-start="9471" data-end="9638">
<p data-start="9474" data-end="9543"><strong data-start="9474" data-end="9503">Continuous-time evolution</strong> (no process change, only field / pops):</p>
<span class="katex-display"><span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" display="block"><semantics><mrow><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mi>P</mi><mo separator="true">,</mo><mi mathvariant="normal">Π</mi><mo separator="true">,</mo><mi>t</mi><mo stretchy="false">)</mo><mover><mo stretchy="true" minsize="3.0em">→</mo><mpadded width="+0.6em" lspace="0.3em"><mrow><mi mathvariant="normal">Δ</mi><mi>t</mi></mrow></mpadded></mover><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mi>P</mi><mo separator="true">,</mo><msub><mi mathvariant="script">E</mi><mrow><mi mathvariant="normal">Δ</mi><mi>t</mi></mrow></msub><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mi mathvariant="normal">Π</mi><mo stretchy="false">)</mo><mo separator="true">,</mo><mi>t</mi><mo>+</mo><mi mathvariant="normal">Δ</mi><mi>t</mi><mo stretchy="false">)</mo><mi mathvariant="normal">.</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">(P, Π, t) \xrightarrow{\Delta t} (P, \mathcal{E}_{\Delta t}(Π), t + \Delta t).</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height: 1.3503em; vertical-align: -0.25em;"></span><span class="mopen">(</span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right: 0.13889em;">P</span><span class="mpunct">,</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right: 0.1667em;"></span><span class="mord">Π</span><span class="mpunct">,</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right: 0.1667em;"></span><span class="mord mathnormal">t</span><span class="mclose">)</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right: 0.2778em;"></span><span class="mrel x-arrow"><span class="vlist-t vlist-t2"><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height: 1.1003em;"><span style="top: -3.322em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height: 2.7em;"></span><span class="sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight x-arrow-pad"><span class="mord mtight"><span class="mord mtight">Δ</span><span class="mord mathnormal mtight">t</span></span></span></span><spa