<h2 data-start="2053" data-end="2106">3. Small-Step Semantics <code data-start="2080" data-end="2086">step</code> (cleaned and total)</h2>
<p data-start="2108" data-end="2194">We’ll parameterize <code data-start="2127" data-end="2133">step</code> by an <strong data-start="2140" data-end="2155">environment</strong> <code data-start="2156" data-end="2167">env : Env</code> so evaluation is explicit.</p>
