<hr data-start="5099" data-end="5102">
<h2 data-start="5104" data-end="5135">5. Well-typed Configurations</h2>
<p data-start="5137" data-end="5189">You already have a <code data-start="5156" data-end="5171">has_type_proc</code>. We just need to:</p>
<ol data-start="5191" data-end="5317">
<li data-start="5191" data-end="5277">
<p data-start="5194" data-end="5277">Make it reasonably complete (add <code data-start="5227" data-end="5235">ty_seq</code>, <code data-start="5237" data-end="5244">ty_if</code>, <code data-start="5246" data-end="5254">ty_let</code>, <code data-start="5256" data-end="5264">ty_fix</code>, <code data-start="5266" data-end="5275">ty_pvar</code>).</p>
</li>
<li data-start="5278" data-end="5317">
<p data-start="5281" data-end="5317">Add a notion of “config well-typed”.</p>
</li>
</ol>
