<ol data-start="192" data-end="525">
<li data-start="192" data-end="325">
<p data-start="195" data-end="325">✔ <strong data-start="197" data-end="239">A corrected &amp; fully consistent version</strong> of your SpherePop.Core file — no logical contradictions, no malformed constructors.</p>
</li>
<li data-start="326" data-end="413">
<p data-start="329" data-end="413">✔ <strong data-start="331" data-end="368">Minimal necessary Lean-side fixes</strong> (purely structural, no change to meaning).</p>
</li>
<li data-start="414" data-end="525">
<p data-start="417" data-end="525">✔ A short explanation of each fix so you can continue building SpherePop semantics without hidden landmines.</p>
</li>
</ol>
<p data-start="527" data-end="591">You can copy/paste the final block directly into a <code data-start="578" data-end="585">.lean</code> file.</p>
<hr data-start="593" data-end="596">
<h1 data-start="598" data-end="622">✅ <strong data-start="602" data-end="622">Key Issues Fixed</strong></h1>
<p data-start="624" data-end="659">Here are the necessary corrections:</p>
<hr data-start="661" data-end="664">
<h2 data-start="666" data-end="717"><strong data-start="669" data-end="717">(1) Record field <code data-start="688" data-end="703">mode : Type u</code> was illegal</strong></h2>
