</li>
<li data-start="4776" data-end="4792">
<p data-start="4778" data-end="4792">BExpr → Bool</p>
</li>
<li data-start="4793" data-end="4815">
<p data-start="4795" data-end="4815">PopExpr → PopParam</p>
</li>
</ul>
<h3 data-start="4817" data-end="4853"><strong data-start="4821" data-end="4851">C. Begin mechanized proofs</strong></h3>
<p data-start="4854" data-end="4888">I can generate Lean skeletons for:</p>
<ul data-start="4890" data-end="5037">
<li data-start="4890" data-end="4958">
<p data-start="4892" data-end="4958"><strong data-start="4892" data-end="4908">Preservation</strong>:<br data-start="4909" data-end="4912">
by induction on the structure of <code data-start="4947" data-end="4957">step_mod</code>.</p>
</li>
<li data-start="4960" data-end="5037">
<p data-start="4962" data-end="5037"><strong data-start="4962" data-end="4974">Progress</strong>:<br data-start="4975" data-end="4978">
via canonical forms lemmas and inversion on typing rules.</p>
</li>
</ul>
<h3 data-start="5039" data-end="5088"><strong data-start="5043" data-end="5086">D. Add operadic semantics for SpherePop</strong></h3>
<p data-start="5089" data-end="5230">This is <em data-start="5097" data-end="5123">highly aligned with RSVP</em>:<br data-start="5124" data-end="5127">
pops form generators, interactions form compositions, and <code data-start="5185" data-end="5195">merge_at</code> becomes the operad multiplication.</p>
