<h3 data-start="7602" data-end="7679"><strong data-start="7606" data-end="7677">C. Connect operad semantics to the <code data-start="7643" data-end="7653">step_mod</code> operational semantics</strong></h3>
<h3 data-start="7680" data-end="7777"><strong data-start="7684" data-end="7775">D. Extend the operad to a <em data-start="7712" data-end="7726">colored PROP</em> supporting linear combinations (entropic flow)</strong></h3>
<h3 data-start="7778" data-end="7865"><strong data-start="7782" data-end="7863">E. Build the Lean proofs that the SpherePop calculus <strong data-start="7837" data-end="7843">is</strong> an operad algebra</strong></h3>
